{"tid":822403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深圳發生7起地面塌陷事故 | 聚焦颱風「山竹」","createTime":"2018-09-16T10:18:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T11:18:30.000Z","uid":141151,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3fba779f6d534e5c1738b35b5dc7426cc1408a9e","tid":822403,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T10:18:03.000Z","msg":"深圳發生7起地面塌陷事故 | 聚焦颱風「山竹」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.sina.com.tw/article/20180916/28205530.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sina.com.tw%2Farticle%2F20180916%2F28205530.html&d=v5teIVfqnhJLvNGsZBJNkTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=8da07681\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.sina.com.tw/article/20180916/28205530.html</a><br />\n<br />\n新京報快訊(記者李玉坤)深圳市規劃和國土資源委剛剛發佈消息，截至今日15時，深圳共發生地面坍塌事故7起，均為一般級地面坍塌事故。<br />\n<br />\n　　地質災害與地面坍塌防治方面，截至9月16日15時，深圳市規劃國土委出動1470人次開展巡查工作，巡查隱患點1041個，共配合轄區疏散轉移1158人、空樓102棟，暫無人員傷亡。共發現地質災害險情1起，位於羅湖金湖山莊後山邊坡，威脅坡下一棟住宅樓，已疏散人數30人。共發現建築邊坡垮塌災情3起，其中羅湖黃貝延芳路變電站邊坡，已做應急處理;葵涌土洋加油站附近一交通邊坡發生垮塌，暫不影響交通;光明區合水口社區金泰格機電廠后建築邊坡發生微型垮塌，垮塌方量約4立方米，無人員傷亡，附近宿舍樓已清空。<br />\n<br />\n　　截至9月16日15時，深圳共發生地面坍塌事故7起，均為一般級地面坍塌事故，其中福田區1起、羅湖區1起、南山區1起、龍崗區1起、寶安區1起、光明區2起，均無人員傷亡。"},{"pid":"25b506744382905e8153496a00ac187bbe489012","tid":822403,"uid":36077,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T10:19:51.000Z","msg":"抵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6511807e4a615474d2082f72981b2d4945b1c2d2","tid":822403,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T10:30:23.000Z","msg":"諗起之前有post話鄰國買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95b44f48574b1c43e6a553cfbc65bf9e83c578e7","tid":822403,"uid":161168,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"25b506744382905e8153496a00ac187bbe489012","tid":822403,"uid":36077,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T10:19:51.000Z","msg":"抵啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T10:33:31.000Z","msg":"重點錯曬，你邊度見到有人傷亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> OK<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你話冇就冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37619dfb4843a466e97b698d7dcea7c9166ae004","tid":822403,"uid":17510,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T10:34:03.000Z","msg":"又話深圳超越香港既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大灣區？不了<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n乜撚野係7起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   7Up<br />\n<br />\n起 係乜撚野量詞黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fc7ce40adb29c9856424e36648be76fe37676fd","tid":822403,"uid":160227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T10:35:18.000Z","msg":"禁多塌陷事件佢贏晒得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6b34173c5cf45a8049e72d5c88747e265769ed0","tid":822403,"uid":35422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T10:38:11.000Z","msg":"咩係7起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"950e0e0cffd416b00fff4405ad1ddf95b3c4aa08","tid":822403,"uid":28800,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T10:47:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be05469408d96dffa82458dd3c688096221181b8","tid":822403,"uid":183601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T10:48:33